hwWlanServiceManagement.name: hwWlanServiceManagement

revisions.description: V1.10 add fwa node in mesh profile.
V1.09 modify the range of hwMeshProfileUrgentHandoverLowRateThreshold node.
V1.07 add mesh profile nodes and statistic nodes.
V1.06 add hwL3RoamInStationCount and hwL3RoamOutStationCount nodes.
V1.04 add new nodes for hwStationTable.
V1.03 add new nodes for hwEssManagementTable,hwStationTable and hwAcStatistics.
V1.02, modify both hwStaStatOperMode and hwMeshProfileMaxLinkNum
V1.02, Add enum value unknown(-1) in hwWlanServiceEssForwardMode of hwEssManagementTable.
V1.03, Add leaf nodes named hwWlanServiceVapBssid in hwVapManagementTable.
